TODO list for BETA PRE implementation
-------------------------------------

1.	Leave/restart out of method-activations
	Branch instructions for leave/restart out of
	method activations, stack unwinding as in
   
        (#
 	do ...
	   L: (# foo: (# do ... leave L; ... #)
                 bar: (# do ... restart L; ... #)
              do ...; bar; ...; fo; ...
              #)
        #)

2.	Misc. array operations: CopyVR1, ExtVR1, ...
        * primitive for copyring an array
        * primitive for extending an array
          
3.	Pattern variables like
	
	   P: (# ... #);
	   S: ^P;
	   R1,R2: ## P;
	do ... P## -> R1##; S## -> R2##;

4.	Byte- and bit operations 
           Shift-operations, ...
	   R.%getByte, ...
	   R.%putBits, ...
	   etc.

5.	Real/floating point

6.	Qua-check (casts) as in:

	   aVechicle[] -> aBus[]

	is currently not implemented

7.	Representation of NONE: 
	Currently NONE is represented as the integer value 0 (zero)
	This should perhaps be changed to use the PRE NULL value.
	A test as in:

		(if NONE // X[] then ... if)

	generates the following code:

		'0 <>: X[]'
	
	'i.e. the reference to X is the argument of the '<>:' message
	send to '0'. This makes the VM fail.

8.	Lots of clean-up:-)

